### Marketing POC - Test Observation Controller Examples

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/tests

### Create a Load Test Result
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "testType": "Load",
  "startTime": "2026-04-08T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-04-08T10:05:00Z",
  "requestCount": 150000,
  "errorCount": 1500,
  "p95Latency": 245.5,
  "avgCpuUsage": 65.2
}

### Create a Stress Test Result
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "testType": "Stress",
  "startTime": "2026-04-08T11:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-04-08T11:02:30Z",
  "requestCount": 250000,
  "errorCount": 8500,
  "p95Latency": 512.8,
  "avgCpuUsage": 89.5
}

### Create a Soak Test Result
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "testType": "Soak",
  "startTime": "2026-04-08T12:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-04-08T12:30:00Z",
  "requestCount": 120000,
  "errorCount": 240,
  "p95Latency": 189.3,
  "avgCpuUsage": 58.7
}

### Get All Test Results
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get All Load Tests
GET {{baseUrl}}?testType=Load

### Get All Stress Tests
GET {{baseUrl}}?testType=Stress

### Get All Soak Tests
GET {{baseUrl}}?testType=Soak

### Get Specific Test Result by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Get Campaigns for Tenant 1
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tenants/1/campaigns?page=1&pageSize=20

### Get Campaigns for Tenant 1 - Page 2
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tenants/1/campaigns?page=2&pageSize=20

### Get Campaigns for Tenant 500
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tenants/500/campaigns?page=1&pageSize=50
